member.summary:
          Embraces the given input string into a properly formed HTML.
          Escape characters will be translated into HTML sequences. Applies the following:

Extended ASCII characters;
                  ElectronicTransaction substitution;
                  Replicate characters;
                  Font size changes to double, quadruple and octuple size;
                  Generates Signature boxes;
                  Text align (Center, Right);
                  Applies font styles (Italic, bold, underline, high density);
                  horizontal tabs and line feeds


Applies available transformations to create an HTML body from a given TextToPrint plain text input.
                   Applies the following: 
                     Extended ASCII characters;
                     ElectronicTransaction substitution;
                     Replicate characters;
                     Font size changes to double, quadruple and octuple size;
                     Generates Signature boxes;
                     Text align (Center, Right);
                     Applies font styles (Italic, Bold, Underline);
                     horizontal tabs and line feeds
